            "restrict_text": "",
            "title": "BIOL 451 Research in Ecology and Development in Africa (3 credits)",
            "overview": "Biology (Sci) : Development of observation and independent inquiry skills through: 1) participation in short-term project modules in collaboration with existing researchers; 2) participation in interdisciplinary team research on topics selected to allow comparative analysis of field sites; 3) active and systematic observation, documentation, and integration of field experience in ecology and development issues.",
            "terms": "Terms: Winter 2020",
