            "prereq_text": "Prerequisites: (<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/comp-250\" target=\"_blank\">COMP 250</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-221\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 221</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-222\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 222</a>), (<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-330\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 330</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-331\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 331</a>) and (<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-351\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 351</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-353\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 353</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-251\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 251</a>)",
