            "prereq_text": "Prerequisites: (<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-304\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 304</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-206\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 206</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-316\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 316</a>) and (<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-305\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 305</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-205\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 205</a>)",
