            "restrict_text": "",
            "title": "ECSE 573 Microwave Electronics (3 credits)",
            "overview": "Electrical Engineering : Physical basis of modern microwave devices and circuits. Microwave transistors and tunnel diodes, transferred electron devices, transit time devices and infra red devices. Microwave generation and amplification, microwave FET circuits. Noise and power amplification.",
