            "title": "MATH 447 Introduction to Stochastic Processes (3 credits)",
            "overview": "Mathematics &amp; Statistics (Sci) : Conditional probability and conditional expectation, generating functions. Branching processes and random walk. Markov chains, transition matrices, classification of states, ergodic theorem, examples. Birth and death processes, queueing theory.",
