            "title": "MATH 545 Introduction to Time Series Analysis (4 credits)",
            "overview": "Mathematics &amp; Statistics (Sci) : Stationary processes; estimation and forecasting of ARMA models; non-stationary and seasonal models; state-space models; financial time series models; multivariate time series models; introduction to spectral analysis; long memory models.",
