            "prereq_text": "Prerequisite: <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/math-350\" target=\"_blank\">MATH 350</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/comp-362\" target=\"_blank\">COMP 362</a> (or equivalent)",
