            "title": "MATH 564 Advanced Real Analysis 1 (4 credits)",
            "overview": "Mathematics &amp; Statistics (Sci) : Review of theory of measure and integration; product measures, Fubini's theorem; Lp spaces; basic principles of Banach spaces; Riesz representation theorem for C(X); Hilbert spaces; part of the material of MATH 565 may be covered as well.",
