            "title": "MATH 571 Higher Algebra 2 (4 credits)",
            "overview": "Mathematics &amp; Statistics (Sci) : Completion of the topics of MATH 570. Rudiments of algebraic number theory. A deeper study of field extensions; Galois theory, separable and regular extensions. Semi-simple rings and modules. Representations of finite groups.",
