            "coreq_text": "",
            "restrict_text": "",
            "title": "MATH 576 Geometry and Topology 1 (4 credits)",
            "overview": "Mathematics &amp; Statistics (Sci) : Basic point-set topology, including connectedness, compactness, product spaces, separation axioms, metric spaces. The fundamental group and covering spaces. Simplicial complexes. Singular and simplicial homology. Part of the material of MATH 577 may be covered as well.",
